Playtesting will go periodically on port 4000.  Whenever new code is installed, it will be playtested on port 4000 for a period of 1 day to 1 week.  If you would like to be a playtester, just log on to meson.atom.com port 4000.  Be sure that you get ahold of staff beforehand, so that they can set you to whatever code is being playtested on port 4000.

 

